/*
 * Prefixes used in the code:
 *
 * `a` - aArray (arrays)
 * `b` - bBlock (code blocks)
 * `c` - cCharacter (strings)
 * `d` - dDate (dates)
 * `l` - lLogical (booleans)
 * `m` - mMemo (memo fields)
 * `n` - nNumeric (numbers)
 * `o` - oObject (objects)
 * `p` - pPointer (pointers)
 * `s` - sSymbol (symbols)
 * `u` - uNIL (undefined or NIL values)
 *
 */

/* Keeping it tidy */
